Slurm

```json
{
  "application": "Slurm",
  "details": {
    "job_name": "dev_concat_fold_10",
    "account": "def-afyshe-ab",
    "nodes": 1,
    "tasks_per_node": 1,
    "gpu": "a100:1",
    "memory": "24000M",
    "time": "4-00:00",
    "cpus_per_task": 3,
    "output": "%N-%j.out",
    "modules": [
      "StdEnv/2020",
      "gcc/9.3.0",
      "cuda/11.4",
      "arrow/5.0.0"
    ],
    "environment_variables": [
      "NCCL_BLOCKING_WAIT=1",
      "MASTER_ADDR=$(hostname)"
    ],
    "python_environment": "dreamscape-qa/env",
    "python_script": "src/re_gold_qa_train.py",
    "script_arguments": [
      "--mode",
      "re_classification_qa_train",
      "--model_path",
      "~/fold_${fold_num}/concat/",
      "--checkpoint",
      "_0_step_${step}_model",
      "--num_search_samples",
      "8",
      "--batch_size",
      "64",
      "--gpu",
      "True",
      "--dev",
      "./zero-shot-extraction/relation_splits/dev.${fold_data_id}",
      "--gpu_device",
      "0",
      "--seed",
      "12321",
      "--concat",
      "True",
      "--prediction_file",
      "~/fold_${fold_num}/concat/relation.concat.dev.predictions.fold.${fold_num}.step.${step}.csv",
      "--predict_type",
      "relation"
    ],
    "script_comments": [
      "steps=(4700 10300 1400 800 14700 1100 2100 800 1300 1600)",
      "steps=(4700)",
      "fold_num=5",
      "fold_data_id=4",
      "step=14700",
      "for (( i=1; i<=525; i++ ))",
      "srun python src/re_gold_qa_train.py"
    ]
  }
}
```
